headline.print_headline: Malawi Electoral Body Challenges President's Annulment of Elections
headline.main: Malawi Electoral Body Challenges President's Annulment of Elections

lead_paragraph: The head of Malawi's electoral authority on Saturday challenged President Joyce Banda's announcement annulling the country's elections, saying she did not have the power to do this and that vote counting was continuing.
